<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.7">
<l>pūvai vaṇṇaṉār puḷḷiṉ mēlvara</l>
<l>mēvi niṉṟunāṉ kaṇṭa taṇṭamō</l>
<l>vīvi laiṅkaṇai villi yampukōt</l>
<l>tāvi yēyilak kāka veyvatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is the punishment [for the fact] that I, [with] continual longing,</l>
<l>Saw him the hue of the [blue] pūvai [blossoms] as he arrived on a bird,</l>
<l>That the archer with five [flower] arrows, nocking his darts,</l>
<l>Ceaselessly shoots at [my] soul as his target?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
